Files in this directory should be copied to the Interact app servers only prod & staging.


The files below should be placed in the /etc/datadog-agent/checks.d directory on the interact-app servers

custom_interact_api_cpu.py
custom_interact_api_freemem.py
custom_interact_api_status.py



The directories below should be placed in the /etc/datadog-agent/conf.d directory on the interact-app servers

http_check.d  # Check the interact http front end
process.d  # Check Java & firewalld processes
tls.d  # SSL cert expiry check.



